;     Change History::
;        Written, 30 Jan 2012. Modeled on ErrPlot from IDL library. David W. Fanning.
;        Added Horizontal keyword. 19 March 2013. Fabien Maussion.
;        Forgot to allow COLOR keyword to be a vector of colors. 18 June 2013. DWF.
;        
; :Copyright:
